*'''Instance naming''' - When creating an [[Special:MyLanguage/Instances#Instance naming|instance]], VRC+ supporters have the option to name it.
*'''Shop discounts''' - VRC+ supporters have the option to purchase [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|shop]] listings for a discount.
*'''VRC+ Supporter [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|Badge]]''' - Being an active supporter of VRC+ will grant a user a "Supporter" badge, as long as their subscription is active. This special badge can be found on your user profile on the platform, and on the VRChat website.
*'''VRC+ [[Badges#VRC+ Tenure badges|Tenure Badge]]''' - Being an active supporter of VRC+ will grant a user a "VRC+ Subscriber" badge, as long as their subscription is active, this badge shows the user's cumulative duration of them being subscribed to VRC+.
*'''VRCat on Quick Menu''' - Clickable VRCat on top of Quick Menu that makes sounds and displays different prompts.
*'''Clock variant''' - Access to use the "VRChat+ Ultra Premium Time ☆" [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu#Clock|clock]] variant.
*'''Reduced display name change cooldown''' {{Upcoming_inline|January 2026|ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-december-18-2025/47354#p-86291-big-things-coming-for-vrc-3}}- Changing display name will be reduced from the normal 3 months cooldown.